Package Collections.Trees

Interface BinaryTreeADT<T>

Type Parameters:
T - the generic type of data element in this tree
All Known Subinterfaces:
BinarySearchTreeADT<T>, HeapADT<T>
All Known Implementing Classes:
ArrayBinarySearchTree, ArrayBinaryTree, ArrayHeap, AVLTree, LinkedBinarySearchTree, LinkedBinaryTree, LinkedHeap, LinkedOrderedBinarySearchTree, PriorityQueue
public interface BinaryTreeADT<T>
BinaryTreeADT defines the interface to a binary tree data structure.
